channel.title: I got a banned account on frugooscape.net but I can't make another 1!
channel.description: Dudes! I made a guy called Killa, he got disabled. And now i put in Ancient Mage and it says, "Invalid username or password" Well how da hell am I supposed to make a new 1?!?!?!?! :confused: :mad: :(
